      <p class="- topic/p ">Before connecting any cables in the system, all cabinets (busbars
and gland plates) must be connected to the protective earth. First
connect the busbar(s) to the protective earth, then connect the gland
plate(s) to the busbar(s). High leakage currents are present when
the system is connected to the mains supplies.</p>
